      • onDeleteProduct

        public void onDeleteProduct​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
        RUNTIME ERROR A run time error occurred before I added lines: 173-176. When the delete button is clicked without a product highlighted it throws a NullPointerException at line 178, because there is no product to evaluate the line SP.getAllAssociatedParts().isEmpty() on. I solved this by moving the (SP=null) check to before the .isEmpty evaluation. Previously I had it in the deleteProduct() method, which is called later. This method is called when Delete button is clicked under the products table.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - Not necessary to specify.
